name: WeGro
public_notice: Project has migrated to a new contract. Please take note of the old contract.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: A community first token with true utility and a unique reflection protocol. WeGro Coin was designed to facilitate a payment/data ecosystem that allows the users to take the data and finance industries and give them back to the people. For the first time ever the power and value of your data is yours to control.
